title: en.wikipedia.org_wiki_List_of_series_run_in_Weekly_Sh%C5%8Dnen_Jump
transformers_text: This is a list of the series that have run in the Shueisha manga anthology book Weekly Sh nen Jump This list is organized by decade and year of each series ' first publication and lists every single notable series run in the manga magazine along with the author of each series and the series ' finishing date if applicable During the changeover of monthly magazines between Monthly Sh nen Jump and Jump SQ in 2007 four monthly series ran stories in the WS J magazine Of the four Claymore ran several one shot extra chapters
